{"tid":2016821,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"(自認股神入)依2個星期升定跌，依波預測到先叫真功夫","createTime":"2020-05-14T16:30:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-15T17:05:16.000Z","uid":84147,"like":60,"dislike":62,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"27aa797ed902e19e82defd9fc62ee12895cfcada","tid":2016821,"uid":84147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T16:30:38.000Z","msg":"牛市個個都係少年股神，中年股聖，同埋廢老巴菲特<br />\n熊市又話熔斷百年一遇唔可以作準<br />\n依家升勢完左，依2個星期好重要，決定左依年牛定熊，Trump選唔選到，什至未來美國國運，依家就係證明自己的機會啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>升(正評):</strong></span></span><br />\n唔好同FED同埋成個美國政府作對，最強印錢機+第一國力玩哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nTrump大選保底點都唔會依家比美股斷，一跌就會長熊去到11月，依家最恐慌時期過撚哂，最多跌埋天日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n新聞出得利空消息先跌點會係想提散戶走為散戶好，一定係大戶又想拉幾日撈一筆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">跌(負評):</span></strong></span><br />\n之前個個係屋企咩都唔知太樂觀，依家復工問題開始出哂黎，失業率加疫症會再爆到9彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n熊市唔會跌一波就完，點都會有第二波，大戶食哂依波升浪就會離場等下一波跌再撈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係時候面對現實，美股估值太高，無可能十年牛一月熊又去番牛，Trump同美國唔好彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34f4e1b9cd92764e9133b6f0b3e08963834a54fa","tid":2016821,"uid":84147,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T16:33:56.000Z","msg":"依2個星期 &gt; 依幾個月 &gt; Trump大選 &gt; 美國政府洗牌 &gt; 美中Trade War &gt; 對待香港問題 &gt; 香港依幾代人命運<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n牛就拜神<br />\n熊就洗定屎忽啦"},{"pid":"d8c8a9cc6048ed3651c6beb3e831526f55307a25","tid":2016821,"uid":263183,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T16:34:53.000Z","msg":"跌"},{"pid":"cc69a5b1021f06341a95d2b469714a7af7216e71","tid":2016821,"uid":84147,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T16:38:17.000Z","msg":"買定離手"},{"pid":"79e3bd6cf8bc98784c73aad7608f21d118967d87","tid":2016821,"uid":84147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T17:34:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d51139408d0fea7bdd1a91734e55a6727059ec5","tid":2016821,"uid":292710,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"27aa797ed902e19e82defd9fc62ee12895cfcada","tid":2016821,"uid":84147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T16:30:38.000Z","msg":"牛市個個都係少年股神，中年股聖，同埋廢老巴菲特<br />\n熊市又話熔斷百年一遇唔可以作準<br />\n依家升勢完左，依2個星期好重要，決定左依年牛定熊，Trump選唔選到，什至未來美國國運，依家就係證明自己的機會啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>升(正評):</strong></span></span><br />\n唔好同FED同埋成個美國政府作對，最強印錢機+第一國力玩哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nTrump大選保底點都唔會依家比美股斷，一跌就會長熊去到11月，依家最恐慌時期過撚哂，最多跌埋天日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n新聞出得利空消息先跌點會係想提散戶走為散戶好，一定係